data.description: This beautiful home is located in the Triad School District of Troy. The main floor has beautiful hardwood floors throughout, a fireplace that is both gas and wood burning, and it also has lovely vaulted ceilings. The eat in kitchen has beautiful granite countertops with a large amount of cabinet space. There is a main floor laundry room off garage. The main floor master has a large master bathroom and a walk in closet. The huge family room in the basement provides extra living space and also has a wet bar, another full bathroom, and a bonus room that could be used as a nonconforming bedroom or an office. The garage is a spacious 2 car attached. The backyard has a nice sized deck and an above ground swimming pool. It should be noted that the house backs up to a field and is currently on a non through street. Roof replaced in 2021.
